{"tid":2273981,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"健身教練涉九龍遊行襲警 事隔16個月被控 今提堂須宵禁","createTime":"2020-11-06T06:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T09:03:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a78b711321dbad1fdd9d1a07256d1ac6be8c5c22","tid":2273981,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:35:20.000Z","msg":"去年7月7日網民發起九龍區大遊行，36歲健身教練涉嫌於當日在亞皆老街襲警，事隔16個月，被控一項襲警及一項抗拒警務人員罪，案件今在西九龍裁判法院提堂。主任裁判官羅德泉應辯方要求，將案件押後至下月17日，被告准以1,500元現金保釋，其間須守宵禁令和禁足令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/FL7F4DJUUREJHIH22WMATKMFA4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FFL7F4DJUUREJHIH22WMATKMFA4%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8vDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=26692a90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FFL7F4DJUUREJHIH22WMATKMFA4%2F&h=16630efb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/FL7F4DJUUREJHIH22WMATKMFA4/</a>"},{"pid":"792423782376d61f2115234811b5fe160aada291","tid":2273981,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d7e3b9e9cc3a51d92a015500b0f51ffb685aa4","tid":2273981,"uid":7369,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"依家日日鳩拉記者同示威者"},{"pid":"ba5eafaa0c952cc5b7b72fd2ea55fb51061ba362","tid":2273981,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"792423782376d61f2115234811b5fe160aada291","tid":2273981,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse